<br>
Now, when AC is the same, and HP isn't quite as much of a concern this is going to mean that monks tank better than pal/SK, and that's not unfair in the least, especially when you consider the amount of work that goes into getting that gear. Can a monk tank Vindi now? Sure, who gives a rat's @$$? Vindi hasn't been high end content for more than a year now. You won't find a monk playing MT for Emp or VT for the same reason a monk didn't MT Vindi a year ago. Balance has been maintained.<br>
<br>
Now, as to why monks make superior rampage tanks? That's easy. FD. It makes for far less chaos due to how VI coded rampage and luclin bosses if a few monks who can turn rampage on/off at will are the rampage tanks. <p>See me at: <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=47953">Schezarine's Sexay Stuff</a>
