<br>
You are making the same mistake most people make: You are comparing <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> composite</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> AC between 2 different classes and using that as an argument about <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> mitigation</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> AC. Find out how much mitigation AC a warrior will have with a composite AC of 1200. Now find out how much mitigation AC a pure caster will have with a composite AC of 900. Things that make you go hrmmm. <p><A href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=14686"> Graal MacBladefury</A><BR>
