exhibit 2:  FD &quot;given because of monks low AC&quot;<br>
exhibit 3:  no taunt button<br>
etc)<br>
... and tanking ability is something they have gained.  they went from a non-tank to a second best or best tank.<br>
<br>
2)  even if verant fixes the balance of mob ATK values vs players' AC's, monks will still be stupidly broken.<br>
<br>
why?<br>
<br>
because of god damn ac 60 magic pajamas.  monks should be limited to class specific armors with ac on par with what you see in every set of monk class specific armors.  (note the low AC)<br>
<br>
remove stupid all/all high ac/hp items , AND re tune mob ATK values vs players' AC's, and the problem will be solved without nerfing monks.<br>
<br>
_____________________________________________<br>
<br>
look, guys, some of my best friends are monks.  but even *they* recognize that they are playing a stupidly overpowered class, given high ac all/all items.<br>
<br>
hell, thats why they picked it: power.<br>
<br>
well... EQ isnt just about power, theres a little thing called *class balance* to consider.<br>
